    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a reliable and comfortable driving experience. While the exterior shows some minor signs of age, such as small stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches consistent with regular use, the body remains solid. The interior is clean and all electronics are fully functional. It\u2019s a dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next owner without needing immediate major repairs.",
