    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The engine is currently running roughly and likely needs a major overhaul, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping between gears. Cosmetically, the exterior shows several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior has heavy staining and tears in the upholstery. This is a project car suited for someone with mechanical expertise or looking for a parts donor.",
