    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and it is in truly mint condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just left the showroom. It\u2019s been pampered, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no stories, just a perfect ride waiting for its next adventure. I\u2019m looking for a smooth sale, so come grab this gem before someone else does! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
