    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that remains in absolute showroom condition. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and treated to regular professional detailing, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero scratches or dents. The interior is equally pristine, featuring smoke-free, unmarked premium leather upholstery and the original factory protective films still present on several trim pieces. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it comes with a complete, documented service history from the authorized dealer and has just received a full multi-point inspection. With low mileage and a smooth, powerful performance that feels brand new, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a top-tier example of this model. Every electronic feature, safety sensor, and luxury amenity functions perfectly.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
